# GAN-Based Image Enhancement

This project uses a Generative Adversarial Network (GAN) to enhance low-light images.

## Features
- Converts dark images into enhanced images
- Uses Generator and Discriminator architecture
- Implemented using TensorFlow and Keras

## Technologies
- Python
- TensorFlow
- OpenCV

## Results
The model successfully improves brightness and visual clarity of low-light images.

## Future Work
- Use larger datasets
- Improve GAN architecture
- Apply for real-world applications like surveillance and medical imaging
